Package: SeroMetrics
Type: Package
Title: Summary Metrics for Antibody Landscapes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bingyi", "Yang", email = "byyang@connect.hku.hk",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Shixian", "Xu", role = "aut"))
Description: Quantitatively summarizes antibody landscapes using metrics that
    capture the magnitude, extent, skewness, and tailedness of antibody response
    profiles. Functions are provided to calculate these metrics from titer data
    and publicly available datasets are included for demonstration.
